[30;1m404 | [0m[35m* `minSuccessPercentage`: percentage of hosts that needs to be healthy in order for the[0m
[30;1m405 | [0m[35m  update to succeed. If you set this value lower than 100, some percentage of hosts may[0m
[30;1m406 | [0m[35m  report failure, while still considering the deployment a success. Default is 100%.[0m
